            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, pat it dry with kitchen paper and finely shred</p><p>Cut your <strong>tomato[es]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>into wedges</p><p>Combine the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (not a fan of raw garlic? Just add a little!) to a bowl with your<strong> mayo</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> – this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
