    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>warmed pitta</strong> with the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>meat-free doner meat</strong>, <strong>sliced red onion</strong> and <strong>tomato wedges</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>garlic mayo</strong> and <strong>chilli sauce</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and serve the <strong>chips</strong> and <strong>remaining garlic mayo </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
